        <button data-cat="DevOps/CI-CD" class="cat-btn px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border bg-card/50 text-muted-foreground border-border/30 hover:border-teal/40 transition-colors cursor-pointer">DevOps/CI-CD</button>
