            <div class="flex-1"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Swiggy Shows Wrong Rider Location</p><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-0.5">WebSocket · Redis Geo · Stale Cache · Event Ordering</p></div>
            <span class="shrink-0 text-muted-foreground text-xs">▼</span>
