          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2 border-t border-border/20 space-y-3">
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-foreground">Root Cause:</strong> Location updates arrive out of order from the mobile app. HTTP retry of an older packet overwrites a newer location stored in Redis, showing the rider teleporting backwards.</p>
            <div class="mermaid text-xs">
sequenceDiagram
  participant App as Rider App
  participant GW as API Gateway
  participant R as Redis GEO
  participant WS as WebSocket
  App->>GW: loc(t=100, lat=12.9, seq=5)
